EG(z) = \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac{s_n}{n!} z^n =  \sum_{n=k}^{\infty} \frac{a^{n-k} z^n}{k!(n-k)!} =  \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac{a^{n} z^{n+k}}{k! n!} = \frac{z^k}{k!}e^{az}\,.
